s also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"borders (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"),  colors (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":")  and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"title":"Theme Orange","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider/sizeMaxHeightAssetsContainer":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token DimensionRawTokens._1200","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"sizeMaxHeightAssetsContainer","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider\/sizemaxheightassetscontainer","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\